quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  43,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  43,1,h m
  43,2,qasam hai iss wazeh kitaab ki
  43,3,ke hum ne isay arabi zabaan ka quran banaya hai taakay tum log isay samjhoo
  43,4,"aur Dur haqeeqat yeh umm al-kitab mein Sabt hai, hamaray haan barri buland martaba aur hikmat se labraiz kitaab"
  43,5,ab kya hum tum se bezaar ho kar yeh dars nasiyaat tumahray haan bhejna chore den sirf iss liye ke tum hadd se guzray hue log ho ?
  43,6,pehlay guzri hui qomon mein bhi baarha hum ne nabi beje hain
  43,7,kabhi aisa nahi howa ke koi nabi unn ke haan aaya ho aur unhon ne uss ka mazaq nah uraya ho
  43,8,"phir jo log inn se bdrj_ha ziyada taaqatwar thay unhen hum ne halaak kar diya, pichli qomon ki misalein guzar chuki hain"
  43,9,agar tum inn logon se pucho ke zameen aur asmano ko kis ne peda kya hai to yeh khud kahin ge ke inhen usi zabardast Aleem hasti ne peda kya hai
  43,10,wohi na jis ne tumahray liye is zameen ko gehwaara banaya aur is mein tumhari khatir rastay bana diye taakay tum apni manzil maqsood ki raah pasko
  43,11,"jis ne aik khaas miqdaar mein aasman se pani utaara aur is ke zareya se murda zameen ko jala uthaya, isi terhan aik roz tum zameen se bar aamad kiye jao ge"
  43,12,"wohi jis ne yeh tamam jore peda kiye, aur jis ne tumahray liye kashtiyon aur janwaron ko sawari banaya taakay tum unn ki pusht par charho"
  43,13,"aur jab unn par betho to apne rab ka ahsaan yaad karo aur kaho ke"" pak hai woh jis ne hamaray liye inn cheezon ko maskhar kar diya warna hum inhen qaboo mein laane ki taaqat nah rakhtay thay"
  43,14,"aur aik roz hamein apne rab ki taraf palatna hai """
  43,15,"( yeh sab kuch jantay aur mantay hue bhi ) inn logon ne uss ke bundon mein se baaz ko is ka juz bana dala, haqeeqat yeh hai ke ensaan khula ahsaan faramosh hai"
  43,16,kya Allah ne apni makhlooq mein se apne liye betiyan intikhab kee aur tumhe beiton se nawaza ?
  43,17,aur haal yeh hai ke jis aulaad ko yeh log uss khuday-e Rehman ki taraf mansoob karte hain uss ki wiladat ka Musda jab khud inn mein se kisi ko diya jata hai to uss ke mun par siyahi chhaa jati hai aur woh gham se bhar jata hai
  43,18,kya Allah ke hissay mein woh aulaad aayi jo zaiwron mein palli jati hai aur behas o Hujjat mein apna mudda poori terhan wazeh bhi nahi kar sakti ?
  43,19,"unhon ne firshton ko, jo khuday-e Rehman ke khaas bande hain, aurtain qarar day liya kya unn ke jism ki saakht unhon ne dekhi hai? inn ki gawahi likh li jaye gi aur inhen is ki jawab dahi karni ho gi"
  43,20,"yeh kehte hain"" agar khuday-e rehman chahta ( ke hum unn ki ibadat nah karen ) to hum kabhi unn ko nah pujte"" yeh is muamlay ki haqeeqat ko qatee nahi jantay, mehez teer tukay lrhate hain"
  43,21,kya hum ne iss se pehlay koi kitaab inn ko di thi jis ki sanad ( apni iss mulaika parasti ke liye ) yeh apne paas rakhtay hon ?
  43,22,"nahi, balkay yeh kehte hain ke hum ne apne baap dada ko aik tareeqay par paaya hai aur hum aُnhi ke naqsh qadam par chal rahay hain"
  43,23,"isi terhan tum se pehlay jis bastii mein bhi hum ne koi Nazeer bheja, uss ke khatay peetay logon ne yahi kaha ke hum ne apne baap dada ko aik tareeqay par paaya hai aur hum aُnhi ke naqsh qadam ki pairwi kar rahay hain"
  43,24,"har nabi ne un se poocha, kya tum usi dagar par chalay jao ge khuwa mein uss rastay se ziyada sahih rasta tumhe batau jis par tum ne apne baap dada ko paaya hai? unhon ne saaray Rasolo-n ko yahi jawab diya ke jis deen ki taraf bulanay ke liye tum beje gay ho hum uss ke kafir hain"
  43,25,aakhir-kaar hum ne unn ki khabar le daali aur dekh lau ke jhutlanay walon ka kya injaam howa
  43,26,"yaad karo woh waqt jab ibrahim ne apne baap aur apni qoum se kaha tha ke"" tum jin ki bandagi karte ho mera unn se koi تعق nahi"
  43,27,"mera talluq sirf uss se hai jis ne mujhe peda kya, wohi meri rahnumai kere ga """
  43,28,aur ibrahim yahi kalma apne peechay apni aulaad mein chore gaya taakay woh iss ki taraf rujoo karen
  43,29,"( is ke bawajood jab yeh log dosaron ki bandagi karne lagey to mein ne un ko mita nahi diya ) balkay mein aِnhin aur inn ke baap dada ko mata hayaat deta raha yahan taq ke inn ke paas haq, aur khol khol kar bayan karne wala rasool agaya"
  43,30,magar jab woh haq inn ke paas aaya to unhon ne keh diya ke yeh to jaadoo hai aur hum is ko maan-ne se inkaar karte hain
  43,31,"kehte hain, yeh quran dono shehron ke barray admion mein se kisi par kyun nah nazil kya gaya ?"
  43,32,"kya tairay rab ki rehmat yeh log taqseem karte hain? duniya ki zindagi mein inn ki guzar busr ke zaraye to hum ne inn ke darmain taqseem kiye hain, aur inn mein se kuch logon ko kuch dosray logon par hum ne bdrj_ha foqiat di hai taakay yeh aik dosray se khidmat len aur tairay rab ki rehmat uss doulat se ziyada qeemti hai jo ( inn ke Raees ) samaitt rahay hain"
  43,33,"agar yeh andesha nah hota ke saaray log aik hi tareeqay ke ho jayen ge to khuday-e Rehman se kufar karne walon ke gharon ki chhatain, aur un ki seedhiyan jin se woh apne baala khaanoon par charhtay hain"
  43,34,"aur unn ke darwazay, aur un ke takhat jin par woh takiye laga kar baithtay hain"
  43,35,"sab chandi aur sonay ke banava dete yeh to mehez hayaat duniya ki mata hai, aur akhirat tairay rab ke ha n sirf muttaqeen ke liye hai"
  43,36,"jo shakhs Rehman ke zikar se taghaful brtta hai, hum is par aik shetan musallat kar dete hain aur woh uss ka Rafeeq ban jata hai"
  43,37,"yeh shyatin aisay logo n ko raah raast par anay se roktay hain, aur woh apni jagah yeh samajte hain ke hum theek ja rahay hain"
  43,38,"aakhir-kaar jab yeh shakhs hamaray haan puhanche ga to apne shetan se kahe ga,"" kash mere aur tairay darmain mashriq o maghrib ka baad hota, too to bad tareen saathi nikla """
  43,39,uss waqt inn logon se kaha jaye ga ke jab tum zulm kar chuke to aaj yeh baat tumahray liye kuch bhi nafea nahi hai ke tum aur tumahray shyatin azaab mein mushtarik hain
  43,40,"ab kya ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum behroon ko sunaaoo ge? ya andhon aur Sarih gumraahi mein parre hue logon ko raah dikhao ge ?"
  43,41,ab to hamein inn ko saza dainee hai khuwa tumhe duniya se utha len
  43,42,"ya tum ko aankhon se inn ka woh injaam dikha den jis ka hum ne inn se wada kya hai, hamein inn par poori qudrat haasil hai"
  43,43,"tum bahar haal uss kitaab ko mazbooti se thaamay raho jo wahi ke zareya se tumahray paas bhaije gayi hai, yaqeenan tum seedhay rastay par ho"
  43,44,haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh kitaab tumahray liye aur tumhari qoum ke liye aik bohat bara Sharf hai aur anqareeb tum logon ko is ki jawab dahi karni ho gi
  43,45,"tum se pehlay hum ne jitne rasool beje thay unn sab se pooch dekho, kya hum ne khuday-e Rehman ke siwa kuch dosray mabood bhi muqarrar kiye thay ke unn ki bandagi ki jaye ?"
  43,46,"hum ne moose ko apni nshanyon ke sath firaon aur uss ke A'ayanesaltanat ke paas bheja, aur is ne ja kar kaha ke mein rab alaalmin ka rasool hon"
  43,47,phir jab uss ne hamari nishanain un ke samnay paish kee to woh thathay maarny lagey
  43,48,"hum aik par aik aisi nishani unn ko dikhata chalay gay jo pehli se barh charh kar thi, aur hum ne unn ko azaab mein dhar liya taakay woh apni rawish se baz ayen"
  43,49,"har azaab ke mauqa par woh kehte, ae sahir, apne rab ki taraf se jo mansab tujhe haasil hai uss ki bana par hamaray liye uss se dua kar, hum zaroor raah raast par aa jayen ge"
  43,50,magar jon hi ke hum un par se azaab hata dete woh apni baat se phir jatay thay
  43,51,"aik roz firaon ne apni qoum ke darmain pukaar kar kaha,"" logo, kya misar ki badshahi meri nahi hai, aur yeh nhrin mere neechay nahi beh rahi hain? kya tum logon ko nazar nahi aata ?"
  43,52,mein behtar hon ya yeh shakhs jo zaleel o haqeer hai aur apni baat bhi khol kar bayan nahi kar sakta ?
  43,53,"kyun nah is par sonay ke kangon utaarey gay? ya firshton ka aik dasta is ki urdali mein nah aaya? """
  43,54,"uss ne apni qoum ko halka samgha aur unhon ne is ki itaat ki, Dur haqeeqat woh thay hi fasik log"
  43,55,aakhir-kaar jab unhon ne hamein ghazab naak kar diya to hum ne un se intiqam liya aur un ko akhatta ghark kar diya
  43,56,aur baad walon ke liye paish ro aur namona Ibrat bana kar rakh diya
  43,57,"aur jounhi ke Ibn maryam ki misaal di gayi, tumhari qoum ke logon ne is par ghul macha diya"
  43,58,"aur lagey kehnay ke hamaray mabood achay hain ya woh? yeh misaal woh tumahray samnay mehez kaj bahsi ke liye laaye hain, haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh hain hi jhagralu log"
  43,59,Ibn maryam iss ke siwa kuch nah tha ke aik bandah tha jis par hum ne inaam kya aur bani Israel ke liye apni qudrat ka aik namona bana diya
  43,60,hum chahain to tum se farishtay peda kar den jo zameen mein tumahray janasheen hon
  43,61,"aur woh darasal qayamat ki aik nishani hai, pas tum uss mein shak nah karo aur meri baat maan lau, yahi seedha rasta hai"
  43,62,aisa nah ho shetan tum ko uss se rok day ke woh tumhara khula dushman hai
  43,63,"aur jab eesa Sarih nishanain liye hue aaya tha to is ne kaha tha ke"" mein tum logon ke paas hikmat le kar aaya hon, aur is liye aaya hon ke tum par baaz unn baton ki haqeeqat khol dun jin mein tum ikhtilaaf kar rahay ho, lehaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo"
  43,64,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah hi mera rab bhi hai aur tumhara rab bhi usi ki tum ibadat karo, yahi seedha rasta hai """
  43,65,"magar ( uss ki iss saaf taleem ke bawajood ) garohoon ne aapas mein ikhtilaaf kya, pas tabahi hai unn logon ke liye jinhon ne zulm kya aik dard naak din ke azaab se"
  43,66,kya yeh log ab bas isi cheez ke muntazir hain ke achanak inn par qayamat aa jaye aur inhen khabar bhi nah ho ?
  43,67,woh din jab aeye ga to muttaqeenko chore kar baqi sab dost aik dosray ke dushman ho jayen ge
  43,68,uss roz unn logon se jo hamari ayaat par imaan laaye thay aur Mutee farmaan ban kar rahay thay
  43,69,"kaha jaye ga ke"" ae mere Bandoo , aaj tumahray liye koi khauf nahi aur nah tumhe koi gham la-haq hoga"
  43,70,"daakhil ho jao jannat mein tum aur tumhari biwiyan, tumhe khush kar diya jaye ga """
  43,71,"unn ke agay sonay ke thaal aur saghar gardish karaye jayen ge aur har mann bhaatii aur nigahon ko lazzat dainay wali cheez wahan mojood ho gi un se kaha jaye ga,"" tum ab yahan hamesha raho ge"
  43,72,tum iss jannat ke waris apne unn aamaal ki wajah se hue ho jo tum duniya mein karte rahay
  43,73,"tumahray liye yahan bakasrat fawaka mojood hain jinhein tum khao ge """
  43,74,"rahay mujrimeen, to woh hamesha jahannum ke azaab mein mubtala rahen ge"
  43,75,"kabhi unn ke azaab mein kami nah ho gi, aur woh is mein mayoos parre hon ge"
  43,76,un par hum ne zulm nahi kya balkay woh khud hi apne oopar zulm karte rahay
  43,77,"woh pukaarain ge,"" ae maalik, tera rab hamara kaam hi tamam kar day to acha hai"" woh jawab day ga,"" tum yun hi parre raho ge"
  43,78,"hum tumahray paas haq le kar aeye thay magar tum mein se aksar ko haq hi nagawaar tha """
  43,79,kya inn logon ne koi iqdaam karne ka faisla kar liya hai? acha to hum bhi phir aik faisla kiye letay hain
  43,80,kya unhon ne yeh samajh rakha hai ke hum inn ki raaz ki baatein aur inn ki sargoshian suntay nahi hain? hum sab kuch sun rahay hain aur hamaray farishtay inn ke paas hi likh rahay hain
  43,81,"inn se kaho,"" agar waqai Rehman ki koi aulaad hoti to sab se pehlay ibadat karne wala mein hota """
  43,82,"pak hai asmano aur zameen ka farmaa rawa arsh ka maalik, unn saari baton se jo yeh log uss ki taraf mansoob karte hain"
  43,83,"acha, aِnhin apne baatil khayalat mein ghark aur apne khail mein munhamik rehne do, yahan taq ke yeh apna woh din dekh len jis ka aِnhin khauf dilaya ja raha hai"
  43,84,"wohi aik aasman mein bhi khuda hai aur zameen mein bhi khuda, aur wohi hakeem o Aleem hai"
  43,85,"bohat baala o bartar hai woh jis ke qabzay mein zameen aur asmano aur har uss cheez ki badshahi hai jo zameen o aasman ke darmain payi jati hai aur wohi qayamat ki gharri ka ilm rakhta hai, aur isi ki taraf tum sab pultay jaane walay ho"
  43,86,"uss ko chore kar yeh log jinhein pkarte hain woh kisi Shafaat ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay, ila yeh ke koi ilm ki bana par haq ki shahadat day"
  43,87,aur agar tum inn se pucho ke aِnhin kis ne peda kya hai to yeh khud kahin ge ke Allah ne phir kahan se yeh dhoka kha rahay hain
  43,88,"qasam hai Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke iss qoul ki ke ae rab, yeh woh log hain jo maan kar nahi dete"
  43,89,"acha, ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se dar guzar karo aur keh do ke salam hai tumhe, anqareeb aِnhin maloom ho jaye ga"
